description: |
    The :tmt:story:`disk hardware requirement </spec/hardware/disk>` can
    no longer be written as a dictionary. This has been a legacy syntax
    that is not used by real-life users anymore.

    .. code-block:: yaml

        # Not supported anymore:
        disk:
            size: 10 GB

        # Correct form:
        disk:
          - size: 10 GB
